I""<h2 id="summary">Summary</h2>

<p>Just a simple demo for login/logout system with Email verification.</p>

<p>Also, deploy for <a href="https://i2x-challenge-demo.herokuapp.com/">Live Demo on Heroku</a></p>

<h2 id="prerequisites">Prerequisites</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Python3
PostgreSQL&gt;=9.4
Mac/Linux
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="use-virtualenv">Use virtualenv</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>python -m venv ENV
source ENV/bin/activate
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="clone-this-repository">Clone this repository</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>git clone https://github.com/vrootic/i2x_challenge.git
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="install-packages">Install packages</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>cd i2x_challenge
pip install -r requirements
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="initialize-db">Initialize DB</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>createdb i2x_challenge
python manage.py migrate
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="create-superuser">Create Superuser</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>python manage.py createsuperuser
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="start-dev-server">Start Dev Server</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>python manage.py runserver
</code></pre></div></div>

<h1 id="deployment-instructions">Deployment instructions</h1>
<h2 id="install-heroku-toolbelt">Install Heroku Toolbelt</h2>
<p>First, <a href="https://signup.heroku.com/">sign up to Heroku</a>
Then, install <a href="https://toolbelt.heroku.com/">Heroku toolbelt</a></p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>heroku login
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="create-heroku-app">Create Heroku app</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>heroku create [your_app_name]
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="set-environment-variables">Set environment variables</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>heroku addons:create heroku-postgresql:hobby-dev
heroku config:set DJANGO_SECRET_KEY='[your secret key]'
heroku config:set DJANGO_SETTINGS_MODULE='config.settings.production'
heroku config:set DJANGO_ALLOWED_HOSTS='.herokuapp.com'
</code></pre></div></div>

<h2 id="push-to-deploy">Push to deploy</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>git push heroku master
</code></pre></div></div>
<h2 id="migrate-the-db">Migrate the DB</h2>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>heroku run python manage.py migrate
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Finish!</p>

<h1 id="link-to-live-demo-on-heroku">Link to live demo on Heroku</h1>

<p><a href="https://i2x-challenge-demo.herokuapp.com/">Live Demo on Heroku</a></p>
:ET